These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, egyptian, polish, australian
4 different games are played: bridge, canasta, backgammon, billiard
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, daffodil, zinnia, amaryllis
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, chaman, ritmeester, baccarat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, techno, trance
City: miami, hamburg, nizza, berlin
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, turtle, rabbit
 1. the nigerian is the game-smoker##1
 2. the fan of trance is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 3. the fan of techno is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 4. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 6. the owner of the cat is the egyptian##1
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 8. the fan of techno is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is the fan of salsa##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who growslily##1
11. the person traveling to miami is the egyptian##1
12. the owner of the pony is the fan of techno##1
13. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the australian##1
14. the person traveling to hamburg is the australian##1
15. the person traveling to berlin is the person who growszinnia##1
16. the nigerian is on the left of the person who growslily##1
17. the polish is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Nationality      | nigerian       | australian      | polish       | egyptian    |
| Game         | bridge    | billiard    | canasta      | backgammon    |
| Flower           | amaryllis | lily       | zinnia | daffodil     |
| Cigar   | game         | ritmeester  | baccarat      | chaman     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa          | trance     | techno       | electronic |
| City         | nizza       | hamburg | berlin       | miami   |
| Pet     | rabbit     | turtle  | pony         | cat   |

